title: Coronavirus: Chinese Super League team return home to Wuhan after 104 days abroad
description: Chinese Super League team Wuhan Zall make an emotional return to their home city after being stuck abroad for three months because of the coronavirus pandemic.
content:
Fans greated the team as they arrived in Wuhan via train
Chinese Super League team Wuhan Zall made an emotional homecoming after being unable to return for three months because of the coronavirus pandemic.
